00:13:41,394 --> 00:13:44,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I just have to get back in front of him!</i></b></font>

141
00:13:51,774 --> 00:13:53,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With this thing's racing capabilities,</i></b></font>

142
00:13:53,714 --> 00:13:55,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can turn the tables in the power section!</i></b></font>

143
00:13:55,884 --> 00:13:57,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just you watch!</i></b></font>

144
00:14:08,094 --> 00:14:11,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've got a two-liter turbo engine,</i>
<i>the fastest on the street racing scene!</i></b></font>

145
00:14:11,964 --> 00:14:15,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no way it'll lose to</i>
<i>some wimpy 1.6-liter engine!</i></b></font>

146
00:14:17,734 --> 00:14:22,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The last part of the course is a
mid-speed section with wide roads.</b></font>

147
00:14:22,074 --> 00:14:24,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is here that the speed
range is raised a notch.</b></font>

148
00:14:24,044 --> 00:14:26,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then the Evo-Six is sure to--</b></font>

149
00:14:26,244 --> 00:14:27,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You never learn, Kenta.</b></font>

150
00:14:27,944 --> 00:14:29,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? But...</b></font>

151
00:14:29,914 --> 00:14:35,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The more their speed increases, the harder
it becomes to accurately gauge braking...</b></font>

152
00:14:35,554 --> 00:14:37,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and the risk factor increases exponentially.</b></font>

153
00:14:37,924 --> 00:14:41,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't that right, big brother?</b></font>

154
00:14:41,424 --> 00:14:47,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the downhill, the importance of technique
over power increases in high-speed areas.</b></font>

155
00:14:57,604 --> 00:15:00,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dammit! It's no good!</i></b></font>

156
00:15:08,584 --> 00:15:10,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That asshole's takin' the</i>
<i>corner without braking!</i></b></font>

157
00:16:14,184 --> 00:16:20,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I... I don't believe it. That racing's incredible...</i></b></font>

158
00:16:42,244 --> 00:16:45,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. Understood.</b></font>

159
00:16:47,454 --> 00:16:53,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Apparently, five or six suspicious-looking cars
are headed this way, coming up toward us.</b></font>

160
00:16:53,724 --> 00:16:56,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do we do, Ryosuke?</b></font>

161
00:16:56,194 --> 00:16:59,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The situation would seem to
preclude our scheduled timed race...</b></font>

162
00:16:59,894 --> 00:17:03,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's get things ready so we can
pull out at a moment's notice.</b></font>

163
00:17:03,464 --> 00:17:06,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The safety of all our team
members is top priority.</b></font>

164
00:17:08,804 --> 00:17:14,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fumihiro, if worse comes to worst,
Keisuke and I will remain behind to buy time.</b></font>

165
00:17:14,314 --> 00:17:17,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You look for an opportunity
to take the others and flee.</b></font>

166
00:17:17,944 --> 00:17:21,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I... Ryosuke...</b></font>

167
00:17:21,254 --> 00:17:26,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought there was a risk of this occurring
during one of our expeditionary races.</b></font>

168
00:17:26,824 --> 00:17:28,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have prepared for the worst.</b></font>

169
00:17:28,324 --> 00:17:31,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just like he said, Fumihiro.</b></font>

170
00:17:31,164 --> 00:17:35,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm used to this sort of thing. Don't worry.</b></font>

171
00:17:35,834 --> 00:17:39,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll find a way to get through this.</b></font>

172
00:17:39,074 --> 00:17:45,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right. In a time like this,
you're our only hope, Keisuke.</b></font>

173
00:17:45,174 --> 00:17:48,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke! I'll stay with you!</b></font>

174
00:17:48,014 --> 00:17:49,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You go along with the others.</b></font>

175
00:17:49,484 --> 00:17:51,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But...</b></font>

176
00:17:51,584 --> 00:17:55,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't let Ryosuke get hurt.
I'm counting on you.</b></font>

177
00:17:55,584 --> 00:17:59,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Just leave it to me.</b></font>

178
00:17:59,294 --> 00:18:01,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke, I'll...</b></font>

179
00:18:01,294 --> 00:18:04,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you worry, Fujiwara.</b></font>

180
00:18:09,864 --> 00:18:11,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There they are.</b></font>

181
00:18:11,104 --> 00:18:14,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Everyone! Get into Vans #1 and #2!</b></font>

182
00:18:54,344 --> 00:18:57,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're gonna watch us a fun little show.</b></font>

183
00:18:57,844 --> 00:19:01,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll get to see that uppity bastard
in the FD cryin' like a girl.</b></font>

184
00:19:01,514 --> 00:19:03,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

185
00:19:03,084 --> 00:19:07,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With a chance like this, we should
join in too, and blow off a little steam.</b></font>

186
00:19:07,024 --> 00:19:10,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, we didn't make
a single yen off of this.</b></font>

187
00:19:10,664 --> 00:19:16,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shit! All the effort we put into this,
and it amounted to nothing.</b></font>

188
00:19:16,864 --> 00:19:18,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's do it!</b></font>

189
00:19:18,834 --> 00:19:24,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, our guy's an ex-motorcycle
gang leader, a real son of a bitch!</b></font>

190
00:19:24,174 --> 00:19:27,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those other guys are gonna get pounded!</b></font>

191
00:19:49,234 --> 00:19:52,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This guy sure looks like a badass...</i></b></font>

192
00:19:52,604 --> 00:19:59,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Supposedly, he's the former leader of some
famous huge gang in northern Kanto!</b></font>

193
00:20:03,744 --> 00:20:05,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't move from there, brother.</b></font>

194
00:21:17,124 --> 00:21:19,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's you, huh?</b></font>

195
00:21:20,394 --> 00:21:24,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was so dark I couldn't tell
it was you at all, Keisuke.</b></font>

196
00:21:24,064 --> 00:21:26,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been too long, sir.</b></font>

197
00:21:28,134 --> 00:21:30,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These guys are friends of yours?</b></font>

198
00:21:30,964 --> 00:21:33,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not keeping very
good company, are you?</b></font>

199
00:21:33,134 --> 00:21:38,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, well, I wouldn't go so far
as to call them "friends."</b></font>

200
00:21:38,404 --> 00:21:40,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They just asked me for a favor...</b></font>

201
00:21:42,344 --> 00:21:47,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bastards! They've done something
rude to you, haven't they?</b></font>

202
00:21:49,524 --> 00:21:54,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess. But it's over with,
so no need to worry about it now.</b></font>

203
00:21:54,324 --> 00:21:57,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>More to the point, your cars
are in the way. Move them.</b></font>

204
00:21:57,764 --> 00:22:00,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm very sorry, I'll do it right now.</b></font>

205
00:22:00,364 --> 00:22:02,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you hear him or what?!</b></font>

206
00:22:02,034 --> 00:22:03,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yessir!</b></font>

207
00:22:15,514 --> 00:22:19,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What gives, Keisuke? You know him?</b></font>

208
00:22:19,384 --> 00:22:26,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, well, I guess he's an old acquaintance
from when I was young and careless...</b></font>

209
00:22:26,054 --> 00:22:28,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My little brother back when
I was still a troublemaker.</b></font>

210
00:22:28,594 --> 00:22:31,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Little brother"?</b></font>

211
00:22:31,064 --> 00:22:36,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, in any case, that was a big help, Keisuke.</b></font>

212
00:22:36,804 --> 00:22:40,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For a while there, I wondered
what would happen to us...</b></font>

213
00:22:40,704 --> 00:22:43,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But now we can go home
without a scratch on us or our cars.</b></font>

214
00:22:43,904 --> 00:22:47,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You certainly are incredible, Keisuke.</b></font>

215
00:22:49,244 --> 00:22:52,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've really made me look bad.</b></font>

216
00:22:52,784 --> 00:22:58,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you not even know who
Keisuke Takahashi is, <i>bitch</i>?!</b></font>

217
00:23:01,724 --> 00:23:04,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On top of that, Project D is so damn cool,</b></font>

218
00:23:04,094 --> 00:23:07,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>everybody in the Gunma
area knows about 'em.</b></font>

219
00:23:07,894 --> 00:23:13,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shitbird, did you forget that <i>I'm</i> from Gunma?!</b></font>

220
00:23:10,434 --> 00:23:12,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Gunma"</b></font>

221
00:23:13,104 --> 00:23:17,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I-I-I didn't know! Please forgive me!</b></font>

222
00:23:17,844 --> 00:23:20,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We didn't know anythin' at all!</b></font>

223
00:23:20,644 --> 00:23:24,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're not even involved so,
uh, please forgive us.</b></font>

224
00:23:24,684 --> 00:23:27,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're friggin' dreamin', cupcake!</b></font>

225
00:23:27,284 --> 00:23:32,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In a bit, I'm gonna teach all you guys a lesson.</b></font>

226
00:23:32,854 --> 00:23:34,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just wait, dammit!!</b></font>

227
00:23:45,634 --> 00:23:50,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As Keisuke's FD is incapable
of functioning normally,</b></font>

228
00:23:50,104 --> 00:23:52,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like to cancel the timed race.</b></font>

229
00:23:52,974 --> 00:23:54,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that all right?</b></font>

230
00:23:54,114 --> 00:23:57,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, it's just fine!</b></font>

231
00:23:57,314 --> 00:24:00,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right, we're moving out!
Everyone, let's go!</b></font>

232
00:24:00,654 --> 00:24:05,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes! We've completely
dominated the Saitama area!</b></font>

233
00:24:56,174 --> 00:25:00,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Somehow, this latest race gave me a hint.</i></b></font>

234
00:25:02,674 --> 00:25:06,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The way to beat it... is this!</i></b></font>

235
00:25:21,194 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A rose that's bloomed on the battlefield,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

236
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A caterpillar that can only move forward</i>
<i>tramples it under foot again today</i></b></font>

237
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, increasing only hatred</i></b></font>

238
00:25:33,374 --> 00:25:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, with those</i>
<i>social conditions transmitted live</i></b></font>

239
00:25:37,484 --> 00:25:46,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hold me with stronger hands</i></b></font>

240
00:25:46,224 --> 00:25:52,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Your voice in a restless night</i>
<i>(For the reason they don't know)</i></b></font>

241
00:25:52,394 --> 00:25:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The world will someday be shedding blood</i>
<i>(All around the world)</i></b></font>

242
00:25:58,464 --> 00:26:08,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let me forget that kind of news,</i>
<i>I don't want to understand</i></b></font>

243
00:26:09,584 --> 00:26:16,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

244
00:26:16,624 --> 00:26:25,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ah, sing gently just a little more, even if it's a lie</i></b></font>

245
00:26:25,164 --> 00:26:29,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Check it, conflicting information is</i>
<i>already reported by the mass media</i></b></font>

246
00:26:29,164 --> 00:26:33,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The outnumbered convey the</i>
<i>deep fears of the whole situation</i></b></font>

247
00:26:33,204 --> 00:26:37,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Reason is flammable, an age</i>
<i>lacking the power of restraint, yeah</i></b></font>

248
00:26:37,204 --> 00:26:41,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Devoting yourself body and spirit,</i>
<i>you keep receiving that baptism</i></b></font>

249
00:26:41,514 --> 00:26:48,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

250
00:26:48,514 --> 00:26:57,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If rowing a boat that's untrustworthy</i>
<i>and on the verge of breaking...</i></b></font>

251
00:26:57,464 --> 00:27:04,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, no one</i>
<i>confess that it was wrong</i></b></font>

252
00:27:04,534 --> 00:27:14,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ah, sing gently just a little more, even if it's a lie</i></b></font>

